test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 3 == 3 and 2 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x789daf3e8940>([74])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x789daf3e8940> = [[1, 74], [1, 74, 1], [74], [74, 1], [1, 74], [1, 74, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x789daf3e8940>([1, 74])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x789daf3e8940> = [[1, 74], [1, 74, 1], [74], [74, 1], [1, 74], [1, 74, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x789daf3e8940>([74, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x789daf3e8940> = [[1, 74], [1, 74, 1], [74], [74, 1], [1, 74], [1, 74, 1], ...].count

 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([])
